name: CHURCHILL
description:
Our world is definitely not flat. It's as round as it can get, a perfect loop of events in an endless cycle of society crumbling through the same choices they make, or refuse to accept. The same plague, the same war, the same death - in BluRay yesterday, today in 4K. Mankind choosing to fall for the same mistakes of the past over and over truly is fascinating to watch. Ssshh! The show's about to start again.

“Those that fail to learn from history are doomed to repeat it.”
- Winston Churchill
